Introduction

Kim Doeun is a South Korean rapper, singer-songwriter, and dancer under BEATS Entertainment and DSP Media. She is best known as the lead rapper of the girl group YOUNG POSSE.

On October 18, 2023, Doeun officially debuted with YOUNG POSSE with the mini album "MACARONI CHEESE EP".
